  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wizard Shrimp™ is a bullet-hell, roguelite game where you play as a Shrimp who is inexplicably also a Wizard?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle your way out of a slimy swamp, escape amethyst caves, before climbing the Mushroom Wizard's Tower to defeat the final boss.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect upgrades and power ups along your quest to become the most powerful Shrimp this world has ever seen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain Krill points to power up your Shrimp and take on the game at harder difficulties in the Cauldron!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel art graphics are accompanied by a modern soundtrack that mixes digital and analogue sounds, embracing naturalistic samples.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your own path out of each area with a unique randomly generated tile system. Leverage your tiles to your tactical advantage by putting a campfire after an enemy encounter. Or say \"f*** it\" and put down only enemy tiles up until the boss, gaining the most amount of power possible but with a higher risk of death!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334500/extras/69bc2dcede4a5c807fec1df060a2abfe.poster.avif?t=1742670206\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334500/extras/69bc2dcede4a5c807fec1df060a2abfe.webm?t=1742670206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334500/extras/69bc2dcede4a5c807fec1df060a2abfe.mp4?t=1742670206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wizard Shrimp™ is a bullet-hell, roguelite game where you play as a Shrimp who is inexplicably also a Wizard?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle your way out of a slimy swamp, escape amethyst caves, before climbing the Mushroom Wizard's Tower to defeat the final boss.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect upgrades and power ups along your quest to become the most powerful Shrimp this world has ever seen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain Krill points to power up your Shrimp and take on the game at harder difficulties in the Cauldron!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel art graphics are accompanied by a modern soundtrack that mixes digital and analogue sounds, embracing naturalistic samples.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your own path out of each area with a unique randomly generated tile system. Leverage your tiles to your tactical advantage by putting a campfire after an enemy encounter. Or say \"f*** it\" and put down only enemy tiles up until the boss, gaining the most amount of power possible but with a higher risk of death!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334500/extras/69bc2dcede4a5c807fec1df060a2abfe.poster.avif?t=1742670206\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334500/extras/69bc2dcede4a5c807fec1df060a2abfe.webm?t=1742670206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334500/extras/69bc2dcede4a5c807fec1df060a2abfe.mp4?t=1742670206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
